    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Loosely organized political group during the French Revolution. The Girondists advocated for the overthrow of the monarchy; ultimately they were supplanted by their rivals, the Montagnards.</Note_Text>
